<div id="find-results">

<p>Select one or multiple chunks of data from the sources below to save in your
cache. Afterwards, pick a cover that you find attractive and all data will then
be saved. You may optionally choose the blank image if no covers are found or
you dislike all of them.</p>

<p>Original Filename: '{{Path}}'</p>

<p><input type="text" id="inTitle" />
	<input type="button" class="but-scrape-research" value="Manual Search" /></p>

<scraper>
<fieldset class="scrape-set" id="scrape-{{Name}}">
<legend><a href="{{Link}}" target="_blank"><img src="{{Icon}}"
	align="absbottom" /> {{Name}}</a></legend>
<div class="results">
<result>
<label><input type="radio" class="find-result" id="sel-{{Name}}"
name="{{Name}}" value="{{id}}" /> {{date}} - {{title}}</label> <a href="{{ref}}" target="_blank">[ref]</a> <br /></result>
</div> <!-- .results -->
</fieldset>
</scraper>

<div id="div-covers">
<img class="scrape-cover" src="modules/movie/img/missing.jpg" alt="No Cover" title="No Cover" />
</div>
</div> <!-- find-results -->
